<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="app-wrapper">
  <%- include('../partials/sidebar') %>
  <div class="main-content">
    <%- include('../partials/topbar', { pageTitle: 'New Task' }) %>
    <%- include('../partials/flash') %>
    <div class="page-content">
      <div class="page-header">
        <div class="page-header-left">
          <h1 class="page-title">Create Study Task</h1>
          <p class="page-subtitle">AI will score and schedule your task automatically</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/planner" class="btn btn-ghost">← Back to Tasks</a>
      </div>

      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.5fr 1fr;gap:24px;align-items:start;">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="card-title">📝 Task Details</div>
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <form action="/planner" method="POST" novalidate>
              <div class="form-grid">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label" for="subject">Subject *</label>
                  <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" class="form-control"
                    placeholder="e.g. Mathematics, Physics" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label" for="topic">Topic *</label>
                  <input type="text" id="topic" name="topic" class="form-control"
                    placeholder="e.g. Integration by Parts" required>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label" for="description">Description</label>
                <textarea id="description" name="description" class="form-control" maxlength="500"
                  placeholder="What specifically needs to be studied or completed?"></textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="form-grid-3">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label" for="deadline">Deadline *</label>
                  <input type="date" id="deadline" name="deadline" class="form-control" required
                    min="<%= new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0] %>">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label" for="estimatedHours">Est. Hours *</label>
                  <input type="number" id="estimatedHours" name="estimatedHours" class="form-control"
                    placeholder="e.g. 3" min="0.5" max="50" step="0.5" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label" for="priority">Priority</label>
                  <select id="priority" name="priority" class="form-control">
                    <option value="low">🟢 Low</option>
                    <option value="medium" selected>🟡 Medium</option>
                    <option value="high">🟠 High</option>
                    <option value="critical">🔴 Critical</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-grid">
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label" for="difficulty">Difficulty Level</label>
                  <select id="difficulty" name="difficulty" class="form-control">
                    <option value="easy">Easy</option>
                    <option value="medium" selected>Medium</option>
                    <option value="hard">Hard</option>
                    <option value="expert">Expert</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <label class="form-label" for="tags">Tags (comma-separated)</label>
                  <input type="text" id="tags" name="tags" class="form-control" placeholder="exam, chapter3, review">
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label" for="notes">Notes</label>
                <textarea id="notes" name="notes" class="form-control" maxlength="1000"
                  placeholder="Additional notes, resources, or reminders..." style="min-height:80px;"></textarea>
              </div>

              <div class="d-flex gap-12" style="margin-top:8px;">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
                  ✦ Create & Schedule with AI
                </button>
                <a href="/planner" class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg">Cancel</a>
              </div>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- AI Info panel -->
        <div>
          <div class="ai-box" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
            <div class="ai-box-label">✦ How AI Scoring Works</div>
            <p style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:14px;">
              The AI engine calculates a priority score based on:
            </p>
            <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);">
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
                <span>⏱ Deadline Urgency</span> <span style="color:var(--accent);font-family:var(--font-mono);">40%</span>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
                <span>🔴 Priority Level</span> <span style="color:var(--accent);font-family:var(--font-mono);">30%</span>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);">
                <span>🧠 Difficulty Level</span> <span style="color:var(--accent);font-family:var(--font-mono);">20%</span>
              </div>
              <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:7px 0;">
                <span>⌚ Estimated Hours</span> <span style="color:var(--accent);font-family:var(--font-mono);">10%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header"><div class="card-title">💡 Study Tips</div></div>
            <div class="card-body" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;">
              <p>• Set realistic deadlines — AI reschedules overdue tasks automatically</p>
              <p>• Use difficulty levels honestly for better scheduling</p>
              <p>• Break large topics into smaller tasks (≤3 hrs each)</p>
              <p>• Add tags to group related tasks for quick filtering</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
